    "Title": "Jorrit Dossier: Updated Energy Anomaly Data",
    "Description": "Hockrow Agency \nCase File #JD10285\nLead Investigator: Arken Mallor\n\nCase Update: \nIt would be helpful to have the most recent energy anomaly data so that we can compare it to what you delivered last time. Any difference between the two data sets could prove useful.\n\nContract Investigator Actions:\nExplore the <EM4>Engineering</EM4> wing and <EM4>retrieve the Energy Anomaly data</EM4> and deliver it to <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4>.\n\nAdditional Notes:\nBe wary of possible hostile forces on site. \n\nTravel to Onyx in a vehicle that can be stored in a large hangar.\n\nOnce you hand off this data, I'll send you a <EM4>ASD Secure Drive</EM4> that you can collect at your home location.",
